values ('hyatt', 'hyatt-aruba', 'Venue 03', 'Hyatt Regency Aruba', 'Palm Beach, Aruba', 'Elegant Tropical Escape', 'var(--coral)', '#E84C3B', 'Hyatt Regency Aruba wedding Palm Beach', 'https://www.hyatt.com/hyatt-regency/en-US/auaru-hyatt-regency-aruba-resort-spa-and-casino', 'hyatt.com', 'https://www.instagram.com/hyattregencyaruba/', '@hyattregencyaruba', 'Upscale, sunset-soaked, and effortlessly tropical — polished without the stiffness.', 'On Aruba''s glamorous Palm Beach, swaying palms and lagoon pools set the scene for sunset ceremonies and refined receptions — the grown-up tropical wedding that still feels like a holiday.', 'It threads the needle: a genuinely upscale beachfront resort that stays relaxed and warm rather than formal. Sophistication with sand between your toes.', 'sunsets here are basically showing off', '["Elegant","Sunset","Luxury","Tropical"]'::jsonb, '[{"ic":"🌅","title":"Sunset beach ceremonies","desc":"Palm Beach faces west — ceremonies time out to a glowing Caribbean sunset backdrop."},{"ic":"🌴","title":"Lush 12-acre grounds","desc":"Multi-level lagoon pools, gardens and a stretch of Aruba''s calmest, prettiest beach."},{"ic":"🥂","title":"Ballroom + open-air spaces","desc":"Elegant indoor ballrooms and breezy oceanfront terraces for receptions of any size."},{"ic":"👸","title":"On-site wedding team","desc":"Dedicated coordinators and customizable packages handle catering, decor and the day-of flow."},{"ic":"🍸","title":"Dining, spa & casino","desc":"Multiple restaurants, a full-service spa, and the on-site Stellaris casino for the night owls."},{"ic":"☀","title":"“One Happy Island” weather","desc":"Aruba sits below the hurricane belt — reliably sunny, perfect for a fall 2028 date."}]'::jsonb, '{"arrival":["resort entrance + palm-lined drive","lagoon pool first impression","oceanfront lobby view","welcome detail on Palm Beach"],"ceremony":["beachfront ceremony at sunset","arch framing the horizon","aisle toward the sea","exchanging rings, golden light"],"reception":["elegant ballroom tablescape","oceanfront terrace dinner","candlelit lounge area","band / dance floor glamour"],"guest":["palapa loungers on Palm Beach","spa relaxation moment","Stellaris casino night","catamaran day trip"],"area":["Palm Beach high-rise strip at dusk","California Lighthouse","Aruba''s desert + divi-divi trees","a vibrant local sunset bar"],"signature":["the signature Aruba sunset","palms against the sky","lagoon pool aerial","toes-in-sand cocktail hour"]}'::jsonb, 3)
